  "text": "## What Is a Complaint?  \nA complaint is any expression of dissatisfaction about our service, products, or actions that requires a response.  \n**Examples:**\n- \"My transfer failed and wasn't refunded\"\n- \"I wasn't informed about a rate change\"\n- \"I was treated poorly in a branch\"\n- \"Your website is difficult to use\"\n- \"A Direct Debit was taken without authorization\"  \n---",
